                  </persName>
            . I am the prisoner Kidson's father. I never sent him for this cloth. I have known Davis six or eight years; he was acquainted with my son.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250630-133-person698">
                  EDWARD 
                  JONES
               <interp inst="t18250630-133-person698" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
